room_title: Escape room "Wild West" by Red Door Escape Room Dallas in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_address: 2600 W 7th Street Suite 114 Fort Worth, TX 76107
room_description: An innocent village in Bollard County needs your help to make a stand against the Brahmin Boys. The boys shot the sheriff dead and locked everyone that could help take them down in the county jail. Set up some dynamite around the bank doors and free the town!
